apps_results.content:
## Question about justice for survivors  
- Reporter asks president about survivors lacking justice  
- President dodges, calls reporter "worst reporter"  

## Wayfair listings and missing girls  
- 4 cases: missing girls, same names on Wayfair cabinets  
- Prices listed: ~$13k, ~$14k, ~$11k, $12k  
- Listings seen as possible link to trafficking, called conspiracy  

## Epstein files and Wayfair/Etsy purchases  
- Wayfair receipt found in Epstein files, dated 06/28/2018  
- Single item, $8,400; item details unknown  
- Missing girl Joanna (Ohio) vanished 5 days earlier  

## WFX company, price changes, Etsy  
- Same WFX storage units now sold for $139  
- Suggestion of unusual, high‚Äëpriced listings on Etsy too  
- No direct proof, but pattern raises suspicion  

## Epstein‚Äôs girlfriend Karina and inheritance  
- Karina described as longtime girlfriend, a dentist  
- Estate signed to her 2 days before Epstein‚Äôs death  
- She allegedly got island, Zorro Ranch, hundreds of millions  

## Casual small talk and daily life  
- Brief chat about football matches timing (spring/summer)  
- Observation of car parking badly on the street  
- Light, non‚Äësubstantive back‚Äëand‚Äëforth, then goodbyes  

## Next steps  
- Investigate official records on Wayfair, WFX transactions  
- Verify Karina‚Äôs identity, role, and inheritance details  
- Cross‚Äëcheck missing persons dates with documented purchases
